description: WHAT A LOCATION for almost 800 pet friendly square feet with private outdoor space in premiere City Point neighborhood straddling Castle Island & The Seaport including beaches, parks & the ever-popular Broadway corridor. Find a dog park across the street, an impressive 15-acre development around the corner plus the convenient start of “T” bus routes 5,7,10 & 11. The cozy living area features a bay window, built-ins and a wood burning fireplace with a pass thru to a gracious galley kitchen. Adjacent you’ll find a wide hallway featuring a separate dining alcove & oversized closet! Efficient 2nd bedroom is ideal for a home office, gym or yoga studio providing direct access to a large private rear deck plus a yard. In unit laundry completes the floor-thru offering. WHAT A PRICE so you really do not want to miss this true opportunity to bring your homeownership love & build equity–it’s easy-peasy with this one! A myriad of unit tenant photos over time are shown but come see for yourself!
